f. is required to allow the landlord, after his prior notice of the date, to inspect the Apartment in order to verify that the Apartment is being used properly and to check that there is no damage to the Apartment.
g. is obliged to protect the facilities and equipment of the Apartment with particular care
VI. Rent extinction
